{"tid":1215044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大鳩撚柒鑊] 如果我哋唔搞清楚呢一點我哋send出外國嘅所謂證據分分鐘變垃圾","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:51:50.000Z","uid":143499,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9f7b880d9ced48924a0d4e46e4fa7ff5bc73883a","tid":1215044,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:56:59.000Z","msg":"香港警察所使用嘅武力及槍械 係根據基本法第232警隊條例入面嘅第四十六即係警隊通例<br />\n<br />\n警隊通例解釋咗警察有乜嘢做得唔做得<br />\n<br />\n警隊通例第29章即:武力與槍械的使用<br />\n<br />\n咁多年嚟都唔公開過，即係我哋根本唔知佢所謂嘅合法權力究竟係乜野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本來我以為黃旗紅旗黑旗橙旗，係佢哋處理示威衝突嘅準則<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如今第29條只有警方先知， 佢一日唔公開就算佢無理開槍殺人你都告佢唔入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇做過警務人員嘅巴打絲打可以分享下第29條究竟講乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警務處正含家剷真係極醜惡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCSrcGO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCSrcGO.png&h=6a98a3ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到使用武力同埋使用槍械嘅條文全部冇撚曬， 我哋根本唔知佢哋開出合唔合法"},{"pid":"c7cfa89fd1de6f96c6289059cd54449fcecea72f","tid":1215044,"uid":4783,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:58:42.000Z","msg":"依家講緊佢違反人權法同國際法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通係expect香港政府會告黑警咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c3d9c4c298090343f2d90a2160f44204bffb31","tid":1215044,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:59:32.000Z","msg":"佢現家仲可以偷改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c57543579efbb73c1e5b188d8766166b0b9e3bf","tid":1215044,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7cfa89fd1de6f96c6289059cd54449fcecea72f","tid":1215044,"uid":4783,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:58:42.000Z","msg":"依家講緊佢違反人權法同國際法<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma